content: The script includes the PA Senate race but that didn't come up in the training- are we talking to voters about that or no?
Are you in the Zoom Phone Bank for PA?  That script does include an ask if they are voting for Bob Casey.
Yes, the Out for Harris NJ bank

Ok, yes I see that particular event.  I do not have the script for that but I suspect if you are calling into PA tonight there is an ask about their voting intention for Senate.  This would be consistent with similar language we are using in DNC phone banks for PA.
And... you can always preview the script to get familiar with the questions/issues we are talking about.
I forgot the script would run along the dialer with me, lol. Sorry about that. Got one strong Harris/Casey so far.
YAY that is great.  Sometimes I get talking and forget to move the script along too!
